    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><dateline>July 2<hi rend="superscript">d.</hi> 1779.</dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>I fear from the appearance of the times there will be no sort of hurry of
                    offering <persName ref="pe0156">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Low’s</persName>
                    book to sale: for I much apprehend that the public can for many years to come
                    attend only to the mere necessaries of life. but still we may try what we can do
                    for I hate despondency. I inclose three plates for <persName ref="pe0058">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Cordiners</persName>
                    <rs ref="ar0236">works</rs> done in this neighborhood. those in <placeName ref="pl0699">London</placeName> are not quite ready; so these had best not
                    shewen till all are come. with the latter will be two for <rs ref="ar0204">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Low’s</rs> which may also be shewen.</p>
                <p>If any feud prevents <persName ref="pe0156">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                        Low</persName> from dedicating to <persName ref="pe0132">Sir L.D.</persName>
                    or any great Scotch patron, I shall not decline the honor.</p>
                <p><persName ref="pe0104">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Gough</persName> will take
                    good care of everything.</p>
                <closer><salute>adieu most sincerely y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">T Pennant</persName></signed></closer>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><address>
                        <addrLine>Mr Paton Custom <gap reason="damage" unit="words" atLeast="1"/></addrLine>
                    </address></p>
                <p><stamp type="postmark">5/IY</stamp></p>
                <p><hi rend="superscript">FREE</hi><persName ref="pe0015">RMostyn</persName></p>
            </div>
        </body>
